ner that is not about technology; but rather, the means in which the future of our \u2018human factories\u2019 are collaboratively defined upon principles founded upon trust.\xA0\xA0"), mdx("p", null, "We are amongst the last of our species who will remember a world without the web. In the interests of bringing about lasting, positive growth for the future of our species and our natural world, the Trust Factory convenes\xA0experts for a once in a lifetime opportunity at the Perth Convention Centre on the 3rd of April 2017 by a collaborative founded upon knowledge of kindness and dignity; which we strive to enshrine for future generations."));
